Introduction

Like Me was a South Korean four-member girl group under Hidden Entertainment. They made their debut on May 24, 2020 with the self-titled single "Like Me". All the members are also cheerleaders and part of Hidden Entertainment's larger cheerleading group, 'Hidden Cheer'.

They are assumed to have disbanded some time in 2023 as their social media accounts have been rebranded.
